---
---

<section class="bg-beige py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-orange font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" data-animation="fade-in">OUR MISSION</p>
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-navy leading-tight" data-animation="fade-up">
        これは単なるサービスではなく、<br />
        日本の中小企業を元気にする<br class="sm:hidden" />「社会貢献活動」です
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Circulation diagram -->
    <div class="animate-on-scroll max-w-xl mx-auto" data-animation="scale-in" data-delay="0.2s">
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Circle items -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-navy/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg">企業が元気に</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-dark/70 mt-1">Healthy Company</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg">働く人々が豊かに</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-dark/70 mt-1">Happy Employees</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-navy/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg">地域・日本全体が良く</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-dark/70 mt-1">Better Society</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-lg">環境変革への寄付</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-dark/70 mt-1">Social Impact</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Circular arrows -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-orange/30" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M50 15 A35 35 0 0 1 85 50" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M85 50 A35 35 0 0 1 50 85" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M50 85 A35 35 0 0 1 15 50" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M15 50 A35 35 0 0 1 50 15" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <polygon points="82,42 90,50 82,50" fill="currentColor"/>
            <polygon points="58,82 50,90 50,82" fill="currentColor"/>
            <polygon points="18,58 10,50 18,50" fill="currentColor"/>
            <polygon points="42,18 50,10 50,18" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-navy mt-8">
        この信念のもと、志を共にする経営者の皆様と、<br />
        新しい形の支援を創り出していきます。
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-dark/40 mt-3">
        ※本サービスの収益の一部は環境保全活動へ寄付いたします。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
